originalSql:
SELECT 
    P.Id AS PostId,
    P.Title,
    P.CreationDate,
    P.ViewCount,
    PT.Name AS PostType,
    U.DisplayName AS OwnerDisplayName,
    COALESCE(V.UpVotesCount, 0) AS UpVotesCount,
    COALESCE(V.DownVotesCount, 0) AS DownVotesCount,
    COALESCE(B.BadgeCount, 0) AS BadgeCount
FROM 
    Posts P
JOIN 
    PostTypes PT ON P.PostTypeId = PT.Id
LEFT JOIN 
    Users U ON P.OwnerUserId = U.Id
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
         PostId, 
         SUM(CASE WHEN VoteTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS UpVotesCount,
         SUM(CASE WHEN VoteTypeId = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DownVotesCount
     FROM 
         Votes
     GROUP BY 
         PostId) V ON P.Id = V.PostId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
         UserId, 
         COUNT(*) AS BadgeCount
     FROM 
         Badges
     GROUP BY 
         UserId) B ON U.Id = B.UserId
ORDER BY 
    P.CreationDate DESC
LIMIT 100

FROM (SELECT "Posts"."Id" AS "POSTID", "Posts"."Title" AS "TITLE", "Posts"."CreationDate" AS "CREATIONDATE", "Posts"."ViewCount" AS "VIEWCOUNT", "PostTypes"."Name" AS "POSTTYPE", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "OWNERDISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t1"."UPVOTESCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."UPVOTESCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "UPVOTESCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t1"."DOWNVOTESCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."DOWNVOTESCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "DOWNVOTESCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t2"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t2"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT"
FROM "Posts"
INNER JOIN "PostTypes" ON "Posts"."PostTypeId" = "PostTypes"."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Users" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "Users"."Id"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "UPVOTESCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "DOWNVOTESCOUNT"
FROM "Votes"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t1" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t1"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId", COUNT(*) AS "BADGECOUNT"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t2" ON "Users"."Id" = "t2"."UserId"
ORDER BY "Posts"."CreationDate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100) AS "t4"
